        "Azure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，两端分别是On-Prem和Azure。本地这边网段是10.20.0.0/16吗？Azure那边呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPrem",
        "Azure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，本地是10.20.0.0/16，Azure VNet用10.10.0.0/16。两边通过IPsec隧道打通。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPrem",
        "Azure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把两个子图画出来，分别标注网段。本地这边需要放哪些组件？",
